('Mercedes-Benz becomes the WTA''s Premier and Exclusive Automobile Partner',
 'Mercedes-Benz has signed a long-term deal to become the Premier Partner and Exclusive Automobile Partner of the WTA, effective 1 January 2026 — described as the most significant partnership in WTA history. The agreement places the Mercedes-Benz brand across the Hologic WTA Tour''s global calendar, from on-court branding to digital and hospitality activations, reaching the tour''s worldwide fanbase. It signals how premium automotive brands are using women''s tennis to build prestige and global reach.',
 'Mercedes-Benz','operator','DE','https://www.wtatennis.com/news/4417616/wta-and-mercedes-benz-announce-long-term-partnership','operator','published','2025-12-10'),
('ATP and EQT announce global partnership through 2030',
 'The ATP has named global investment organisation EQT its first official private markets partner and a Platinum Partner through 2030. EQT activates across ATP Masters 1000, 500 and 250 tournaments throughout the season, connecting the brand with a global tennis audience of more than one billion fans. For EQT it is a long-runway platform for sustained international brand exposure tied to elite men''s tennis.',
 'EQT','operator','SE','https://www.atptour.com/en/news/atp-eqt-partnership-announcement-june-2026','operator','published','2026-06-09'),
('Verizon lands landmark U.S. partnership with the ATP and WTA Tours',
 'Verizon became the first telecommunications partner of the ATP and the official telecoms partner of both tours for U.S. events, in a multi-year agreement that secures category exclusivity in 5G. The deal gives Verizon integrated visibility across the U.S. tournament calendar and Tennis Channel properties under one package. It is a template for how a single brand can own a category across the American tennis season.',
 'Verizon','operator','US','https://www.atptour.com/en/news/verizon-announcement-2025','operator','published','2025-05-12'),
('Tennis Channel and Sinclair open a single U.S. sponsorship gateway for the ATP and WTA',
 'Sinclair and its Tennis Channel announced a first-of-its-kind partnership letting sponsors access both the ATP and Hologic WTA U.S. calendars plus all Tennis Channel platforms under one comprehensive package. The structure lowers the barrier for brands to reach U.S. tennis audiences across broadcast, streaming and on-site at once. Verizon was unveiled as the first integrated sponsor under the model.',
 'Tennis Channel (Sinclair)','operator','US','https://www.sportsvideo.org/2025/05/09/sinclair-atp-wta-and-u-s-based-tennis-tournaments-announce-sponsorship-partnership-verizon-signs-multi-year-agreement-as-first-integrated-sponsor/','operator','published','2025-05-09'),
('PIF and EQT named official partners of the 2026 HSBC Championships',
 'Saudi Arabia''s Public Investment Fund (PIF) and EQT have become official partners of the LTA''s Queen''s Club Championships, staged as the HSBC Championships. The multi-year deals add global investment brands to one of the grass season''s marquee events, with on-site and broadcast exposure in the run-up to Wimbledon. It underlines how heritage British tennis is attracting major international sponsors.',
 'Public Investment Fund (PIF)','operator','GB','https://www.lta.org.uk/news/2026/june/new-atp-global-partners-announced-for-2026-hsbc-championships/','operator','published','2026-06-05'),
('HSBC becomes title sponsor of the Queen''s Club Championships',
 'The LTA named HSBC the new title sponsor of the Queen''s Club Championships, which now runs as the HSBC Championships. The naming-rights deal puts HSBC front and centre across one of the most prestigious grass-court events on the calendar, from court branding to broadcast mentions. Title sponsorship of a heritage event remains one of the highest-visibility assets in tennis.',
 'HSBC','operator','GB','https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Queen%27s_Club_Championships','operator','published','2025-07-02'),
('Nitto Denko extends ATP Finals title partnership through 2030',
