('Carlos Alcaraz tops 2025 endorsement earnings with a deep brand roster',
 'According to Last Word on Sports, Carlos Alcaraz led tennis off-court income in 2025 with roughly $35m in endorsements on top of prize money, anchored by Nike and partners including Rolex, Louis Vuitton and BMW. The numbers illustrate how a single tennis star can deliver category-spanning exposure for apparel, luxury, automotive and watch brands simultaneously.',
